title: Serial Killers & Frankincense | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 26
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


THE BABES are finally back in the same room!!! YASSSS! This episode is EXTRA! They talk serial killers, frankincense, John Alite being on Chris' podcast Chrissy Chaos, getting tan, new scents, how many people have you met have murdered someone? How many serial killers are there? What did Chris do in LA with Chazz Palminteri?! ALL THIS AND MORE ON TODAY'S HEY BABE!!


Rate us on iTunes!
